---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Maison Interiors">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex-1 w-full">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-foreground mb-8">About Maison Interiors</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-muted-foreground font-light leading-relaxed">
      <p>Maison Interiors is a premier digital publication dedicated to architectural theory, spatial psychology, and high-end interior design for the modern home.</p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-foreground mb-3 mt-8">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Founded by Mikael Garbo, our mission is to bridge the gap between abstract architectural concepts and practical, livable spaces. We believe that a well-designed environment is not merely an aesthetic choice, but a fundamental component of cognitive well-being and daily functionality.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Rather than simply following fleeting trends, we analyze the structural integrity, historical context, and psychological impact of design choices. From the grounding effects of mid-century modern earth tones to the acoustic physics of brutalist raw concrete, our editorial team dissects the 'why' behind the 'what'.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-foreground mb-3 mt-8">Editorial Standards</h2>
        <p>Our content is driven by rigorous research and empirical design testing. Every article published on Maison Interiors undergoes a strict editorial process to ensure high information gain, accuracy, and actionable value for homeowners, architecture enthusiasts, and professional designers alike.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>